{"tid":1802903,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唔聲唔聲嚇你一驚 原來馬明佢...","createTime":"2019-12-29T19:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T20:42:12.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a467c55e513e36fcaaf6049b910a718bfdf91000","tid":1802903,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:59:55.000Z","msg":"係一名總理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有生還者表示，客機出事前曾經激烈搖晃，撞到建築物後傳出巨響，機艙內一片漆黑，乘客要用手機照明。事故後，有近十名乘客協助救出其他被困的人。<br />\n<br />\n總統托卡耶夫主持內閣會議，將周六定為全國哀悼日；<span style=\"color: red;\">又委派總理馬明領導調查委員會</span>，在下月10日提交初步調查報告。<br />\n<br />\n副總理斯克利亞爾表示，飛機起飛時機尾曾兩度觸及跑道，顯示起飛時已出現困難。當局已找到客機俗稱「黑盒」的飛行紀錄儀，將循人為或機件故障方向調查事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa7c2927c645e0946c52f558b19d69c912407d2","tid":1802903,"uid":44916,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T20:03:04.000Z","msg":"弱智先拎呢啲新聞笑"},{"pid":"00a44221221773948370b7612d9f757f04e99c36","tid":1802903,"uid":3705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T20:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJsrTRd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJsrTRd.jpg&h=7563a9a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80cae4a5dea368a5f01999ebc03bf1f50c67d9df","tid":1802903,"uid":52339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T20:05:20.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"70f4696de72d1b5857594d878aab9842dd81d0f7","tid":1802903,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"daa7c2927c645e0946c52f558b19d69c912407d2","tid":1802903,"uid":44916,"like":16,"dislike":0,"